#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2910
msgid "All local outputs, in sync"
msgstr "Tutte le uscite locali, in sincronia"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2927
msgid "Plays on every connected speaker at the same time — wired outputs are delayed to stay in step with Bluetooth."
msgstr "Riproduce su tutti gli altoparlanti collegati contemporaneamente — le uscite cablate vengono ritardate per restare al passo con il Bluetooth."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2941
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2948
msgid "Sync fine-tune"
msgstr "Regolazione fine della sincronia"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2958
msgid "If the Bluetooth speaker still trails the wired ones, raise this until they play together."
msgstr "Se l'altoparlante Bluetooth resta indietro rispetto a quelli cablati, alza questo finché non suonano insieme."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2976
msgid "Calibrate with the microphone"
msgstr "Calibra con il microfono"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2981
msgid "Plays a few loud clicks through each speaker and measures with the microphone how far the Bluetooth speaker trails — the delay is set automatically."
msgstr "Riproduce alcuni clic forti da ogni altoparlante e misura col microfono quanto ritarda l'altoparlante Bluetooth — il ritardo si imposta da solo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3001
msgid "Round 1 of 2 — clicks through every speaker…"
msgstr "Fase 1 di 2 — clic da ogni altoparlante…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3002
msgid "Round 2 of 2 — quiet, checking the result…"
msgstr "Fase 2 di 2 — silenzio, verifica del risultato…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3032
msgid "%1 plays in the group"
msgstr "%1 suona nel gruppo"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3045
msgid "Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr "Se questo altoparlante suona nel gruppo — deseleziona per lasciarlo fuori senza disconnetterlo. Memorizzato per il dispositivo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3051
msgid "%1 (nothing plugged in)"
msgstr "%1 (niente collegato)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3061
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "Bilanciamento di %1"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3070
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr "La quota di questo altoparlante nel volume — il bilanciamento segue ogni movimento del volume principale e viene ricordato per il dispositivo. Agisce solo su ciò che riproduce questo widget; il volume per dispositivo nelle impostazioni audio di sistema è un livello separato e intatto — per questo quei numeri differiscono da questi cursori."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3087
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3088
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3089
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
msgid "M"
msgstr "M"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3090
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays plain stereo"
msgid "ST"
msgstr "ST"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3095
msgid "Which channels this speaker plays: stereo, left only, right only, or a mono mix of both. Set one speaker to L and another to R for a true stereo pair — remembered for the device."
msgstr "Quali canali riproduce questo altoparlante: stereo, solo sinistro, solo destro o un mix mono di entrambi. Imposta un altoparlante su L e un altro su R per una vera coppia stereo — memorizzato per il dispositivo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3125
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3140
msgid "Bluetooth is off or no adapter is available — check System Settings."
msgstr "Il Bluetooth è spento o nessun adattatore è disponibile — controlla le Impostazioni di sistema."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3151
msgid "No paired Bluetooth audio devices — pair the speaker once in System Settings and it appears here."
msgstr "Nessun dispositivo audio Bluetooth associato — associa l'altoparlante una volta nelle Impostazioni di sistema e apparirà qui."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3165
msgid "%1 — connecting…"
msgstr "%1 — connessione…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3183
msgid "%1 — pairing…"
msgstr "%1 — associazione…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3184
msgid "%1 — new, click to pair"
msgstr "%1 — nuovo, fai clic per associare"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3195
msgid "Pair a new speaker…"
msgstr "Associa un nuovo altoparlante…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3211
msgid "Searching — put the speaker in pairing mode…"
msgstr "Ricerca — metti l'altoparlante in modalità associazione…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3232
msgid "WiFi & network"
msgstr "WiFi e rete"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3264
msgid "%1 (speaker group)"
msgstr "%1 (gruppo di altoparlanti)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3292
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Bilanciamento"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3306
msgid "This device's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device."
msgstr "La quota di questo dispositivo nel volume — il bilanciamento segue ogni movimento del cursore principale e viene ricordato per il dispositivo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3328
msgid "Each device buffers on its own, so rooms may play a few seconds apart. For perfectly synced speakers, group them in the Google Home app — the group appears here as a single device."
msgstr "Ogni dispositivo memorizza il flusso per conto proprio, quindi le stanze possono suonare con qualche secondo di differenza. Per altoparlanti perfettamente sincronizzati, raggruppali nell'app Google Home — il gruppo appare qui come un unico dispositivo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3338
msgid "Stop casting everywhere"
msgstr "Ferma la trasmissione ovunque"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3356
msgid "Searching for devices…"
msgstr "Ricerca di dispositivi…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3365
msgid "No devices found on your network"
msgstr "Nessun dispositivo trovato nella rete"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3387
msgid "Volume: %1% (scroll to adjust)"
msgstr "Volume: %1% (scorri per regolare)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/Heading.qml:37
msgid "Back to stations"
msgstr "Torna alle stazioni"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/Heading.qml:126
